title: Free Agency Day 3: Russell Wilson, Trent Williams, & A.J. Green
itunes:title: Free Agency Day 3: Russell Wilson, Trent Williams, & A.J. Green
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you the latest news on the first day of the new league year. Free Agency Day 3 is in full swing and there are some more big moves to talk about! The Seahawks turned down a pretty big offer for Russell Wilson and Gregg Rosenthal's top free agent, Trent Williams, is off the board (21:19). A.J Green has a new home (24:59) and Emmanuel Sanders is wracking up his frequent flyer miles (34:31). We break down piggy banks (37:50) and if they have to be animals before heading into some much needed 8 o'clock delight (41:04).
